357
00:29:16,989 --> 00:29:19,354
- Oh, you're right.
- Yes.

358
00:29:19,379 --> 00:29:21,400
Mm, I understand completely.

359
00:29:21,425 --> 00:29:23,414
Just a baseless rumor.

360
00:29:23,439 --> 00:29:25,136
