361
00:29:25,161 --> 00:29:27,859
I'll call the publisher.

362
00:29:27,884 --> 00:29:29,291
I'll make a call too.

363
00:29:29,316 --> 00:29:31,439
- Please.
- Please.

364
00:29:31,464 --> 00:29:33,477
