495
00:41:16,853 --> 00:41:17,853
Uh...

496
00:41:19,310 --> 00:41:20,310
Akafuji.

497
00:41:21,813 --> 00:41:23,619
A talking hallucination?

498
00:41:26,226 --> 00:41:27,226
Eh?

499
00:41:30,052 --> 00:41:31,761
Don't tell me

500
00:41:31,786 --> 00:41:33,414
you're my fan.

501
00:41:34,589 --> 00:41:37,050
I'm neither a fan or a stan.

502
00:41:37,649 --> 00:41:39,823
He's someone I'm secretly in love with.

503
00:41:42,454 --> 00:41:43,454
Wait.

504
00:41:43,935 --> 00:41:44,935
Hm?

505
00:41:45,636 --> 00:41:47,222
Hmm?

506
00:41:56,479 --> 00:41:57,479
Eh?

507
00:42:00,134 --> 00:42:01,247
The real...

508
00:42:02,820 --> 00:42:04,229
Hajime Aoyanagi?

509
00:42:05,390 --> 00:42:06,390
Real?

510
00:42:08,218 --> 00:42:10,522
Oh, sorry for coming unannounced.

511
00:42:11,905 --> 00:42:12,905
Uh...

512
00:42:13,765 --> 00:42:16,782
I needed to talk to you
about something in person.

513
00:42:24,775 --> 00:42:27,328
Oh, Akafuji! Wait!

514
00:42:30,988 --> 00:42:32,216
Akafuji!

515
00:42:36,994 --> 00:42:38,073
Akafuji!

516
00:42:45,630 --> 00:42:46,630
Akafuji!

517
00:42:49,152 --> 00:42:51,267
Wait! Akafuji!

518
00:42:56,413 --> 00:42:57,413
Wait!

519
00:42:59,552 --> 00:43:00,815
Akafuji!

520
00:43:02,091 --> 00:43:04,161
Akafuji, wait!

521
00:43:08,586 --> 00:43:09,586
Ow.

522
00:43:11,055 --> 00:43:13,347
Mr. Hajime, are you okay?

523
00:43:58,970 --> 00:44:00,131
Seven years ago,

524
00:44:01,971 --> 00:44:02,971
do you remember

525
00:44:03,598 --> 00:44:06,254
running into a high-school geek here?

526
00:44:07,778 --> 00:44:08,778
Oh.

527
00:44:09,184 --> 00:44:10,184
Mm.

528
00:44:18,797 --> 00:44:19,797
That kid...

529
00:44:22,509 --> 00:44:23,653
was me!

530
00:44:25,480 --> 00:44:26,480
Eh?

531
00:44:29,634 --> 00:44:30,858
Oh!

532
00:44:40,475 --> 00:44:41,959
At the time,

533
00:44:43,217 --> 00:44:48,269
I thought other people's words had hurt me.

534
00:44:50,352 --> 00:44:52,279
So I acted tough,

535
00:44:53,217 --> 00:44:56,159
thinking despite being rejected
by people around me,

536
00:44:57,128 --> 00:44:58,451
as long as I stayed myself

537
00:44:59,597 --> 00:45:02,261
and accepted my own interests,
that was enough.

538
00:45:03,581 --> 00:45:06,940
Thinking back now,
I'm embarrassed by my naivety.

539
00:45:13,133 --> 00:45:15,289
That's why I was so happy

540
00:45:17,119 --> 00:45:18,445
that you...

541
00:45:19,354 --> 00:45:20,700
said to me...

542
00:45:21,652 --> 00:45:22,842
"I like it."

543
00:45:29,559 --> 00:45:30,895
Ever since that day,

544
00:45:34,165 --> 00:45:38,890
I sought out all past works
of Hajime Aoyanagi.

545
00:45:41,311 --> 00:45:44,490
I watched all your dramas
and the variety shows you went on.

546
00:45:46,036 --> 00:45:47,171
I became...

547
00:45:50,036 --> 00:45:52,026
a Hajime Aoyanagi stan.

548
00:45:58,093 --> 00:45:59,093
But...

549
00:46:02,660 --> 00:46:03,980
not anymore.

